comment: /**  * Specify if the cache should be cleared before invoking the method. By default, the  * cache is cleared after the method invocation.  * @see javax.cache.annotation.CacheRemoveAll#afterInvocation()  */
code: /**  * Specify if the cache should be cleared before invoking the method. By default, the  * cache is cleared after the method invocation.  * @see javax.cache.annotation.CacheRemoveAll#afterInvocation()  */ public boolean isEarlyRemove() {     return !getCacheAnnotation().afterInvocation(). }
